    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RHI prediction accuracy within 15% across all five operating points. The assessment team accepted the validation evidence generated under build 2026-q1-build-7-rc2 as applicable to the released build 2026-q1-build-7, characterizing the difference as a patch-level release-candidate suffix with no solver-level changes. No re-execution of validation under the released build was performed or required by the team. Overall credibility assessment: Medium assurance level achieved, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II CPB device.",
